{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0f8f6b0f11","title":"对陆定一家属来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b102ad638a","index":0,"year":1975,"month":9,"day":28,"articleId":"0f8f6b0f11"}],"tags":[{"id":"107051c4e6","name":"陆定一","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/52-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji52":{"comments":[{"id":"8a4e640a50","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"0f8f6b0f11","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陆定一，原任中共中央政治局候补委员、中央书记处书记、中央宣传部部长、国务院副总理兼文化部部长。“文化大革命”中被错误地打成所谓“彭、罗、陆、杨反党集团”成员，受到残酷迪害。1979年6月8日，中共中央转发中组部《关于陆定一同志问题的复查报告》，为他平反昭雪。"},{"id":"26b1cfdf10","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"0f8f6b0f11","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陆定一的子女1975年中秋节请中共中央副主席、国务院副总理邓小平转交他们写给毛泽东的一封信，信中转达了陆定一被关押之前对毛泽东所表达的坚定信念，并期望毛泽东再次搅救他们的父亲。"},{"id":"516e3014ad","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"0f8f6b0f11","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"小平，即邓小平。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8d6d2a263f","type":"title","text":"对陆定一家属来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"0f8f6b0f11"},{"id":"8a4e640a50","type":"paragraph","text":"请小平同志商有关同志，研究一下，提出意见告我。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"0f8f6b0f11"},{"id":"26b1cfdf10","type":"paragraph","text":"九月廿八日","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"0f8f6b0f11"}],"page":{"id":"65a8e02a28","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"0f8f6b0f11","start":74,"end":74}}}},"__N_SSG":true}